org.mozilla.taskcluster.client.secrets

Class Secrets

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mozilla.taskcluster.client.TaskClusterRequestHandler
      • org.mozilla.taskcluster.client.secrets.Secrets

  • public class Secrets
extends TaskClusterRequestHandler

    The secrets service, is a simple key/value store for secret data guarded by TaskCluster scopes. It is typically available at secrets.taskcluster.net.

    See: http://docs.taskcluster.net/services/secrets
